# Images Directory

This directory contains all images used on the website.

## Usage

Images in the `public` folder are served at the root path. For example:
- `public/images/logo.png` → `/images/logo.png` in your code
- `public/images/hero-bg.jpg` → `/images/hero-bg.jpg` in your code

## Recommended Structure

```
public/
├── images/
│   ├── logo.png
│   ├── favicon.ico
│   ├── hero/
│   │   └── hero-image.jpg
│   ├── about/
│   │   └── team-photo.jpg
│   └── resources/
│       └── resource-icon.svg
```

## Image Optimization Tips

- Use WebP format for better compression
- Optimize images before adding them
- Use appropriate sizes for different screen resolutions
- Consider using responsive images with `srcset`

